SELECT T.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S AS PMOTN_REQ_ID,O.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S,T.CRT_UPDT_USER_ID FROM IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T O,IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T T 
WHERE T.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S=O.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S

SELECT OPORI.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S AS PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T OPORI
WHERE OPORI.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S IN (SELECT TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO WHERE TPROO.PROC_STAT_CD=6 AND TPROO.LST_UPDT_DTTM<SYSDATE-1)

SELECT OPORI.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S AS PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T OPORI
WHERE OPORI.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S IN (SELECT TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO WHERE TPROO.PROC_STAT_CD=6 AND TPROO.LST_UPDT_DTTM<SYSDATE-1)

select OPORI.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S as PROMO_ID, 
UHILV.BRD_ID,
TPROO.MKT_ID, 
TPROO.CHNL_ID,
UHILV.DIV_ID,
UHILV.DEPT_ID,
TPROO.MDSE_LVL_CD,
TPROO. CRT_UPDT_USER_ID
from 
IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T OPORI, 
IPTCGI.UHILV_UNIV_HIER_LVL_T UHILV, 
IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO,
IPTCGI.PRPLA_PMOTN_REQ_PMOTN_LVL_T PRPLA 
where
OPORI.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S = TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S and
TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S = PRPLA.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S and
PRPLA.MDSE_HIER_LVL_SEQ_NBR_S = UHILV.UNIV_HIER_LVL_SEQ_NBR_S

SELECT OPORI.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S AS PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T OPORI
WHERE OPORI.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S IN (SELECT TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO WHERE TPROO.PROC_STAT_CD=6 AND TPROO.LST_UPDT_DTTM<SYSDATE-1)
SELECT TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO WHERE TPROO.PROC_STAT_CD=6 AND TPROO.LST_UPDT_DTTM<SYSDATE-1

SELECT OPORI.PMOTN_GRP_ID_S AS PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.OPORI_OUTB_PMOTN_REQ_GRP_T OPORI
WHERE OPORI.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S IN (SELECT TPROO.PMOTN_REQ_ID_S FROM IPTCGI.TPROO_PMOTN_REQ_HDR_OTPT_T TPROO WHERE TPROO.PROC_STAT_CD=7 AND TPROO.MDSE_LVL_CD=4 AND TPROO.LST_UPDT_DTTM>=SYSDATE-1)
